cs.CL, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing techniques applied to programming languages.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a likely category as the paper proposes a new approach for software development tasks that involve translating programs written in one language to another.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses neural network-based techniques for producing word embeddings and learning cross-language vector representations.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes an automated approach for program translation.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a possible category as the paper deals with cross-language mappings for various kinds of structural code elements.
